{"tid":2390864,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"GME股價收市瀉3成 盤後再瀉1成至200美元水平 沽空倉位已大減逾半","createTime":"2021-02-02T00:35:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-02T06:08:50.000Z","uid":25345,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c1f7137b9ddff38c71b90be61faa67b76137ae50","tid":2390864,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T00:35:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2868327/%E3%80%90%E9%81%8A%E6%88%B2%E9%A9%9B%E7%AB%99GME%E3%80%91GME%E8%82%A1%E5%83%B9%E6%94%B6%E5%B8%82%E7%80%893%E6%88%90%E3%80%80%E7%9B%A4%E5%BE%8C%E5%86%8D%E7%80%891%E6%88%90%E8%87%B3200%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E6%B0%B4%E5%B9%B3%E3%80%80%E6%B2%BD%E7%A9%BA%E5%80%89%E4%BD%8D%E5%B7%B2%E5%A4%A7%E6%B8%9B%E9%80%BE%E5%8D%8A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2868327%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E9%2581%258A%25E6%2588%25B2%25E9%25A9%259B%25E7%25AB%2599GME%25E3%2580%2591GME%25E8%2582%25A1%25E5%2583%25B9%25E6%2594%25B6%25E5%25B8%2582%25E7%2580%25893%25E6%2588%2590%25E3%2580%2580%25E7%259B%25A4%25E5%25BE%258C%25E5%2586%258D%25E7%2580%25891%25E6%2588%2590%25E8%2587%25B3200%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E3%2580%2580%25E6%25B2%25BD%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E5%2580%2589%25E4%25BD%258D%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25B8%259B%25E9%2580%25BE%25E5%258D%258A&d=FyOxfEvlGqeE3CGJWKQQl%2Fhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=526787ba\" target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2868327/%E3%80%90%E9%81%8A%E6%88%B2%E9%A9%9B%E7%AB%99GME%E3%80%91GME%E8%82%A1%E5%83%B9%E6%94%B6%E5%B8%82%E7%80%893%E6%88%90%E3%80%80%E7%9B%A4%E5%BE%8C%E5%86%8D%E7%80%891%E6%88%90%E8%87%B3200%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E6%B0%B4%E5%B9%B3%E3%80%80%E6%B2%BD%E7%A9%BA%E5%80%89%E4%BD%8D%E5%B7%B2%E5%A4%A7%E6%B8%9B%E9%80%BE%E5%8D%8A</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2865000/2868327/RTS20210129_MDF13631_1024.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2865000%2F2868327%2FRTS20210129_MDF13631_1024.JPG&h=fe56fb1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n遊戲驛站GameStop（美︰GME）股價急瀉，一度跌113美元或35%，低見212美元，並觸發熔斷，收市報225.01美元，跌99.99美元或30.8%。收市後股價再瀉1成，至200美元水平。數據公司S3表示，超過3500萬股GameStop的淡倉已被平倉，淡倉只剩下有2710萬股，即淡倉已減逾半。<br />\n<br />\n全日成交回落至88.02億美元。值得留意的是，GME所標榜的是散戶對大鱷，不過，在最近數個交易日的成交達百億美元，明顯不只散戶在操作，最高峰為上周三，成交達293.26億美元，相當於2272.8億港元，超越港股成交額。<br />\n<br />\n沽空機構減半淡倉後，被挾的壓力已大幅縮減，故仍持有2710萬股淡倉，可留有後着，若股價重回年初被挾前的十多美元水平，當中有約300美元的差價，可追回不少損失，不過應難達到；若由即市跌幅99.99美元計，剩下的淡倉作用已發揮，可補回不少損失。<br />\n<br />\n各地近期有不少散戶表示入貨，若散戶近期才入貨，預期已接火棒，損手或不輕。<br />\n<br />\n外電引述IHS Markit數據顯示，針對GME的沽空倉位，由1月中佔自由流通股的114%銳減到39%。另一家市場數據公司S3 Partners的數據也相近，GameStop沽空倉位數量已經降到相當於自由流通股數的50%左右。儘管數據本身可能與實際有些許差異，但可能初步表明推動挾倉的力量及動機已經減弱。"},{"pid":"ff77e158a83d5d5a945a321e2c5a84aae57bf392","tid":2390864,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T00:37:28.000Z","msg":"完喇 世界回復和平<br />\n正義大戶又一次消滅邪惡散戶"},{"pid":"c13b33dcf71bcc622e71da4f4d14328568f9e925","tid":2390864,"uid":199318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T01:12:10.000Z","msg":"酒呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29259c8a2b61830ae26a7abf9bf42fb5bd2a7568","tid":2390864,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T02:32:45.000Z","msg":"FAKE NEWS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f59ea31b279baa29d3b58cdad06dfcbc241a8c75","tid":2390864,"uid":103668,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T06:08:50.000Z","msg":"尋日成交37M<br />\n即係咁<br />\n全部平倉黎架？<br />\n我入個d咩貨黎"}]}